}

}

}

}

table.example_values {
    border: 0;
}

.example_values th {
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #555;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.example_values tr, .example_values td {
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #555;
}

table.stats, table.sample, table.duplicate{
    border: 0;
}

.stats tr, .sample tr, .duplicate tr {
    border: 0;
}

.stats th, .stats td{
    color: #555;
    border: 0;
}

.stats th {
    padding: 0 2em 0 0;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.stats td {
    padding: 1px;
}

table.sample, table.duplicate{
    margin-bottom: 2em;

}

.sample td, .sample th, .duplicate td, .duplicate th {
    padding: 0.5em;

}

.sample thead, .duplicate thead {
    border-top: 0;

}

.sample td, .duplicate td {
    width: 100%;
}

.histogram {
    margin-top: 3em;
}

/* Freq table */
table.freq {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    border: 0;
}

table.freq th, table.freq tr, table.freq td {
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.freq thead {
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;

}

/* Freq mini */
.freq.mini td {
    width: 50%;
    padding: 1px;
    font-size: 12px;

}

table.freq.mini {
    width: 100%;
}

.freq.mini th {
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
    max-width: 5em;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 0.5em;
}

.missing {
    color: #a94442;
}

.alert, .alert > th, .alert > td {
    color: #a94442;
}

.ignore {
    opacity: 0.4;
}

/* Bars in tables */
.freq.table{
    table-layout: fixed;
}

.freq:not(.mini) tr td:nth-child(1), .freq:not(.mini) tr th:nth-child(1){

    max-width: none;

    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
}

.freq:not(.mini) tr td:nth-child(2), .freq:not(.mini) tr td:nth-child(3), .freq:not(.mini) tr th:nth-child(2), .freq:not(.mini) tr th:nth-child(3){

}
.freq:not(.mini) tr td:nth-child(4), .freq:not(.mini) tr th:nth-child(4){

}

    width: 0;
    height: 100%;

    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #337ab7;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-right: 4px;
}

    background-color: #999;
}

.missing .bar {
    background-color: #a94442;
}

.tooltip-inner {
    width: 100%;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-align: left;
}

.extrapadding {
    padding: 2em;
